Page Type#

You can specify the pageType in the frontmatter metadata to use different
layouts in the page. By default, the pageType of the document is doc, so the
sidebar on the left and the outline on the right will appear by default. If you
don't need these, you can set pageType to custom:

---
pageType: custom
